Lead project development from 0 to 1 for SGE EDS System and IOM Case Management System. 
 In SGE EDS System project, design complex solutions including case management system, online application portal and ETL solution to automate SG Enable’s working process; 
 In IOM Case Management System project, design and deliver integrated systems to fulfill IOM’s (International Organization for Migration) needs for content managing (Dynamic CRM 2016) and a crowd funding portal (SharePoint 2016).
